There is not any single distance not even one small step worth going towards the falsity that is &quot;love&quot;.<br>
<br>
Now let me explain myself.<br>
<br>
A year ago I would have said what ever distance or what ever steps it took. But over this past year  I have been shown, like layers of flesh slowly peeled away to reveal the deeper workings, That love is all just falsity on lie on more falsity. Love as everyone thinks of it simply does not exist. I have seen &quot;perfect&quot; couples I have seen &quot;soul mates&quot;, and yet all I have ever really seen was falsity. <br>
I know I have never felt love I have felt attraction, a deeper sense of wanting, a lust. But no nothing I have ever felt can be called love. Love does not hurt you. Love does not inspire you to want to hurt others. Love is pure, perfect and unfaltering. I can tell you all 3 of those things do not exist there for love does not.<br>
If I have offended anyone that was not my intent but I knew its a possibility, and I am not sorry. Most of all you don't have to agree. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.cox.net/vual/pictures/reaper-vual.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
